## Dataset Structure

| Dataset | Purpose | Layer |
|---------|---------|-------|
| `prod_edm_main` | Main modelling layer | Facts and Dimensions |
| `prod_edm_prerequisites` | Prerequisites/staging | Intermediate transforms |
| `prod_edm_presentation` | Presentation layer | Final tables for reporting |

## Key Tables

